+//         Also dirty everything on drop.
+// Fix 2: Zoom scale — calculate_close_z() now accounts for output aspect
+//         so the panel fills the screen exactly on both axes.
 
 ===== CHANGE 1 of 3 — in cube_render_instance_t::schedule_instructions() =====
